LOGIN-PAGE.LEFT-SECTION.HEADING: Dear Families,
LOGIN-PAGE.LEFT-SECTION.CONTENT.PARA1: Welcome to the NAVY CYP 1Core Child and Youth Program Business Modernization System (NAVY CYP 1Core) Director Portal. The Director Portal allows you to securely manage your family's profile to include program registration and payment information.
LOGIN-PAGE.LEFT-SECTION.CONTENT.PARA2: NAVY CYP 1Core implemented MFA (Multi-factor Authentication) using DoD recommended Okta Verify solution. All the NAVY CYP 1Core users will require Okta Verify account to login. We will slowly phase out the Username/Password login from CYPBMS.
LOGIN-PAGE.LEFT-SECTION.CONTENT.PARA3: If you don't have an Okta account or need more information on Okta, Please contact parentsupport@afcyptest.com (or) 1-855-975-2266.
